    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, there are noticeable signs of wear on the interior and some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior. It may require some minor maintenance or cosmetic touch-ups in the near future, but it remains a solid choice for daily commuting or as a secondary vehicle.",
