    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly 'as-is,' making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or a parts donor. The engine is currently non-operational and requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission exhibits severe slipping. Externally, the body shows significant rust perforation on the rocker panels, multiple large dents, and heavily faded paint. Inside, the cabin has seen better days, with ripped upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and most of the electronic components, including the radio and AC, currently failing to function. Prospective buyers should plan to have the vehicle towed.",
      "price": 4500.0,
